CONTEXT CompositionTypeMismatchCheck IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT CompositionTypeMismatchCheck
{+ This test must fail because meet(C,A) does not exist.
   The target of result[A*C] and the target of r[A*B];r[A*B]~ do not match. +}

RELATION r[A*B]
RELATION result[A*C]

RULE testCompositionFail: result = r;r~

ENDCONTEXT
